  WHEN budat = '00000000' THEN NULL
  ELSE TO_TIMESTAMP (budat, 'yyyyMMdd')

CASE
  WHEN cpudt = '00000000' THEN CAST(NULL AS TIMESTAMP)
  ELSE to_timestamp (concat(cpudt, cputm), 'yyyyMMddHHmmss')
END

CASE
  WHEN bldat = '00000000' THEN NULL
  ELSE to_timestamp (bldat, 'yyyyMMdd')
END
